    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-transparent"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 md:py-20">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold font-heading tracking-tight dark:text-white sm:text-5xl mb-8">About me</h2>
        <div class="text-lg dark:text-slate-300 text-center space-y-4">
          <p>
            My career began in <span class="text-orange-600 font-bold">mechatronic engineering</span>, where I learned
            the discipline of building systems that simply work—robustly and predictably. That analytical foundation is
            my starting point.
          </p>
          <p>
            As a <span class="text-orange-600 font-bold">full-stack developer</span>, I discovered my passion for
            building digital products people love to use. I understood that behind every interface there's a person,
            and that empathy for the end user is as crucial as clean code.
          </p>
          <p>
            Now, as an <span class="text-orange-600 font-bold">AI/ML specialist</span>, I'm at the forefront of
            training next-generation AI models, having evaluated <strong>168,000+ lines of AI-generated code</strong>
            and completed <strong>560+ training tasks</strong> with a 90% approval rating.
          </p>
          <p>
            This triad—<span class="text-orange-600 font-bold">engineering rigor</span>,
            <span class="text-orange-600 font-bold">user-centered development</span>, and
            <span class="text-orange-600 font-bold">AI expertise</span>—is my unique method. I deliver solutions that
            are technically sound, intuitive to use, and powered by cutting-edge technology.
          </p>
          <p class="italic text-center pt-4">Want to see this approach in action?</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center">
          <a
            href="https://es.fiverr.com/villegas296"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="group flex items-center gap-3 px-6 py-3 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-200 dark:border-slate-700 hover:border-orange-600 dark:hover:border-orange-600 w-full sm:w-auto justify-center"
          >
            <div
